title: First Amish
description:
First Amish, written by Caitlin Tegart. Stone Cold Fox at Maude Night, UCBTNY, March 10, 2008.

Starring Sean Clements, D'Arcy Erokan, Fran Gillespie, Nate Lang, Cody Melton, & Joe Spellman. Directed by Dominic Dierkes.
